{"tid":937753,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我一直以為自己好獨特，但原來我只係一件垃圾","createTime":"2018-12-11T19:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T04:42:44.000Z","uid":167330,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"57be1e98f5719c4a5754636fe37cb3cae7c12262","tid":937753,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T19:19:57.000Z","msg":"以為自己總有一日會叻過身邊所有人，<br />\n<br />\n以為呢個世界只有我有抱負，<br />\n<br />\n以為我嘅失敗都同其他人唔同，人哋失敗因為佢哋真係一件垃圾，而我只係未開竅，未肯發奮。<br />\n<br />\n以為年紀到咗，自然會有女朋友，<br />\n<br />\n以為自己總會出人頭地，但我做唔到。<br />\n<br />\n我同自己講，唔一定要出類拔萃，只有做個有用嘅人就夠，但我都做唔到。<br />\n<br />\n總係冇動力，身邊嘅人都好努力，當初坐喺同一個房室嘅同學，而家已經讀緊神科。<br />\n<br />\n當初暗戀好耐嘅女神，俾醫科生溝走咗，<br />\n<br />\n就算我努力，可能都只係喺office做牛做馬做到死，因為我浪費咗最好嘅光蔭，甚至我連咁嘅機會都冇<br />\n<br />\n原來我一直以嚟都太自負<br />\n<br />\n我可能係全世界最垃圾嗰20%，將來可能仲廢<br />\n<br />\n可能呢個世界，真係要有我呢啲廢人墊底<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知而家活著同死有乜分別，<br />\n<br />\n但我怕死<br />\n<br />\n一事無成<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OprbPw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OprbPw.png&h=83755483&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MjR5snS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMjR5snS.png&h=31c73451&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a201553b6984ce9db9721200647f3b6c7d851d6c","tid":937753,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T19:28:17.000Z","msg":"巴打我同你完全一樣<br />\n而家後悔莫及<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5feb34073ed223b6ff9375486c1be7e2ee5e2e09","tid":937753,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a201553b6984ce9db9721200647f3b6c7d851d6c","tid":937753,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T19:28:17.000Z","msg":"巴打我同你完全一樣<br />\n而家後悔莫及<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T19:32:17.000Z","msg":"但自問就算時光倒流返到以前，應該都係會重蹈覆轍，因為而家已經不斷重覆緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876e2c88e8d2c5d60566ec85e6a48a1246792ad4","tid":937753,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T21:54:45.000Z","msg":"冷靜D照下鏡,睇下自己個樣, 同埋睇下你本銀行存摺有幾多錢先啦   世界好公平   如果人人都心想事成  會天下大亂  世上總要有你D咁既廢人"},{"pid":"99225201d59625c935978e6f4260493e8338aa7d","tid":937753,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"876e2c88e8d2c5d60566ec85e6a48a1246792ad4","tid":937753,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T21:54:45.000Z","msg":"冷靜D照下鏡,睇下自己個樣, 同埋睇下你本銀行存摺有幾多錢先啦   世界好公平   如果人人都心想事成  會天下大亂  世上總要有你D咁既廢人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T00:40:31.000Z","msg":"我都估到一定會見到呢篇潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b86596145ae76bf639c55c3f851108d46018499","tid":937753,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T04:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQ5eoQy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQ5eoQy.png&h=1de883c4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}